<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ZOSIA — 大地是底色，山嶺是恩典，晨星是盼望，方舟是智慧。</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --brown: #9a7b5b;
    --green: #5e8c52;
    --orange: #d98e0a;
    --blue: #3a7abf;
    --bg: #faf9f6;
    --bg-warm: #f5f0e8;
    --text: #2d2a26;
    --text-light: #6b6560;
    --text-muted: #9a948d;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== NAV ===== */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 24px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(250, 249, 246, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  nav.scrolled {
    padding: 16px 48px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 36px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 80%, rgba(154,123,91,0.04), transparent),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 20%, rgba(58,122,191,0.03), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 120px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-bars {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.2s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-bar {
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
  }

  .hero-bar:nth-child(1) {
    width: 160px;
    background: var(--brown);
    animation: barGrow 0.8s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }
  .hero-bar:nth-child(2) {
    width: 90px;
    background: var(--green);
    animation: barGrow 0.8s ease 0.75s forwards;
  }
  .hero-bar:nth-child(3) {
    width: 72px;
    background: var(--orange);
    animation: barGrow 0.8s ease 0.9s forwards;
  }
  .hero-bar:nth-child(4) {
    width: 28px;
    background: var(--blue);
    animation: barGrow 0.8s ease 1.05s forwards;
  }

  .hero-poem {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .hero-poem .line {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3.5vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--text);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-poem .line:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
  .hero-poem .line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }
  .hero-poem .line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.8s; }
  .hero-poem .line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 2.1s; }

  .c-brown { color: var(--brown); }
  .c-green { color: var(--green); }
  .c-orange { color: var(--orange); }
  .c-blue { color: var(--blue); }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 3s forwards;
  }

  .hero-scroll span {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--text-muted);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ===== PHILOSOPHY ===== */
  .philosophy {
    padding: 140px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .philosophy-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .philosophy-text h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .philosophy-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  /* ===== COLORS SECTION ===== */
  .colors-section {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .colors-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .colors-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .colors-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .colors-header p {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .colors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .color-card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 40px 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
  }

  .color-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .color-swatch {
    width: 100%;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .color-card-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .color-card-en {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .color-card-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .color-card-verse {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    padding-top: 20px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* ===== PRODUCTS ===== */
  .products {
    padding: 140px 48px;
  }

  .products-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .products-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .products-header h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .product-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .product-card {
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
  }

  .product-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  .product-card:nth-child(1)::before {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(154,123,91,0.08), rgba(154,123,91,0.02));
  }
  .product-card:nth-child(2)::before {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(94,140,82,0.08), rgba(94,140,82,0.02));
  }
  .product-card:nth-child(3)::before {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(58,122,191,0.08), rgba(58,122,191,0.02));
  }

  .product-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .product-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .product-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 32px;
    left: 32px;
    opacity: 0.15;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }

  .product-card:hover .product-icon { opacity: 0.3; }

  .product-name {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .product-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    position: relative;
  }

  .product-bar {
    width: 32px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ===== BRAND STATEMENT ===== */
  .statement {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--bg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .statement::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 15% 85%, rgba(154,123,91,0.1), transparent),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 30% 30% at 85% 15%, rgba(58,122,191,0.08), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .statement-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    color: rgba(250,249,246,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .statement-text {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 2.2;
    max-width: 600px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .statement-bars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 56px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .statement-bars .bar {
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .statement-bars .bar:nth-child(1) { width: 60px; background: var(--brown); }
  .statement-bars .bar:nth-child(2) { width: 36px; background: var(--green); }
  .statement-bars .bar:nth-child(3) { width: 28px; background: var(--orange); }
  .statement-bars .bar:nth-child(4) { width: 12px; background: var(--blue); }

  /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
  footer {
    padding: 60px 48px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .footer-right {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-right a {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .footer-right a:hover { color: var(--text); }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes barGrow {
    from { transform: scaleX(0); }
    to { transform: scaleX(1); }
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scaleY(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scaleY(1.15); }
  }

  /* scroll reveal */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }

    .hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
    .hero-bars { gap: 10px; }
    .hero-bar:nth-child(1) { width: 100px; }
    .hero-bar:nth-child(2) { width: 56px; }
    .hero-bar:nth-child(3) { width: 44px; }
    .hero-bar:nth-child(4) { width: 18px; }

    .philosophy { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .philosophy-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .colors-section { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .colors-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .products { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .products-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .product-card { aspect-ratio: auto; padding: 28px; }

    .statement { padding: 100px 24px; }
    footer {
      padding: 40px 24px;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .footer-right { gap: 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">ZOSIA</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#philosophy">品牌理念</a></li>
    <li><a href="#colors">四色家譜</a></li>
    <li><a href="#products">產品系列</a></li>
    <li><a href="#statement">關於我們</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-logo">ZOSIA</div>
  <div class="hero-bars">
    <div class="hero-bar"></div>
    <div class="hero-bar"></div>
    <div class="hero-bar"></div>
    <div class="hero-bar"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-poem">
    <div class="line"><span class="c-brown">大地</span>是底色，</div>
    <div class="line"><span class="c-green">山嶺</span>是恩典，</div>
    <div class="line"><span class="c-orange">晨星</span>是盼望，</div>
    <div class="line"><span class="c-blue">方舟</span>是智慧。</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>SCROLL</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
<section class="philosophy" id="philosophy">
  <div class="philosophy-inner reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Philosophy</div>
    <div class="philosophy-text">
      <h2>每一個家，<br>都值得被好好整理。</h2>
      <p>ZOSIA 相信：秩序不是束縛，而是自由的起點。當生活有了結構，愛才有空間展開。我們為家庭設計工具，讓日常的混亂變成可以被擁抱的節奏。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COLORS -->
<section class="colors-section" id="colors">
  <div class="colors-header reveal">
    <h2>四色家譜</h2>
    <p>一個家庭的四種底色，一個品牌的基因密碼</p>
  </div>
  <div class="colors-grid">
    <div class="color-card reveal">
      <div class="color-swatch" style="background: var(--brown);"></div>
      <div class="color-card-en">Earth</div>
      <div class="color-card-title c-brown">大地</div>
      <div class="color-card-desc">底色。<br>在一切被畫上去之前，<br>先有這一層。</div>
      <div class="color-card-verse">國王與王后，<br>根基與起點。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="color-card reveal">
      <div class="color-swatch" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
      <div class="color-card-en">Zion</div>
      <div class="color-card-title c-green">山嶺</div>
      <div class="color-card-desc">恩典。<br>安靜地矗立在那裡，<br>不搖動。</div>
      <div class="color-card-verse">活在恩典之中，<br>錫安・至高之處。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="color-card reveal">
      <div class="color-swatch" style="background: var(--orange);"></div>
      <div class="color-card-en">Zenith</div>
      <div class="color-card-title c-orange">晨星</div>
      <div class="color-card-desc">盼望。<br>在至高之處照亮眾人，<br>引領方向。</div>
      <div class="color-card-verse">在至高之處，<br>榮耀歸與上帝。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="color-card reveal">
      <div class="color-swatch" style="background: var(--blue);"></div>
      <div class="color-card-en">Zosia</div>
      <div class="color-card-title c-blue">方舟</div>
      <div class="color-card-desc">智慧。<br>承載信心，<br>跨越風浪。</div>
      <div class="color-card-verse">使波浪的響聲，<br>都平靜了。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PRODUCTS -->
<section class="products" id="products">
  <div class="products-inner">
    <div class="products-header reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Products</div>
      <h2>為家庭而生的工具</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="product-grid">
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="product-bar" style="background: var(--brown);"></div>
        <div class="product-name">家庭計畫本</div>
        <div class="product-desc">週計畫、月目標、年度回顧——一本讓全家人對齊節奏的手帳。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-icon">📦</div>
        <div class="product-bar" style="background: var(--green);"></div>
        <div class="product-name">收納標籤系統</div>
        <div class="product-desc">可重複書寫的磁吸標籤，讓每一個空間都有名字。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-icon">⚓</div>
        <div class="product-bar" style="background: var(--blue);"></div>
        <div class="product-name">成長紀錄卡</div>
        <div class="product-desc">每一張卡片記錄一個里程碑，孩子的成長不只是照片。</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATEMENT -->
<section class="statement" id="statement">
  <div class="statement-logo">ZOSIA</div>
  <div class="statement-text">
    我們不是幸運湊在一起的名字，<br>
    而是被呼召走同一條道路的家人。<br><br>
    我們有國王、王后、山城、晨星、方舟——<br>
    在恩典裡，朝著盼望前行。
  </div>
  <div class="statement-bars">
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <div class="bar"></div>
    <div class="bar"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-logo">ZOSIA</div>
  <div class="footer-right">
    <a href="#">Instagram</a>
    <a href="#">Facebook</a>
    <a href="#">鷹家買物社</a>
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 ZOSIA. 鷹式一家</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  // Nav scroll effect
  const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 60);
  });

  // Scroll reveal
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.15 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>

